{"tid":210499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"常秘開會看遊日資訊捱轟","createTime":"2017-04-21T03:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T04:31:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d57396ece69f7c6fb7767bd4bc8616b51eb1a6","tid":210499,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19996415&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19996415%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=33383691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19996415%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&h=fd6f70e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19996415&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421</a><br />\n<br />\n常秘開會看遊日資訊捱轟<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會工務小組委員會昨討論南港島線（東段）主要基建工程及沙嶺墳場興建骨灰安置所等項目時，發展局常任秘書長（規劃及地政）黃偉綸（圖）被傳媒發現以近一小時觀看Google Map和日本旅遊資訊。<br />\n黃偉綸會後被問到相關資料是否與會議有關時坦言「同個會冇直接關係」；問及做法是否不恰當，黃面帶尷尬說「我諗留畀大家評論啦」，繼而離開立法會。<br />\n黃偉綸昨午2時半至6時45分出席立法會工務小組委員會，會上甚少機會須回應議員提問，最終會議只通過南港島線的撥款，沙嶺項目則至會議結束前仍未能表決。有傳媒拍到黃與會期間埋首看旅遊資料，黃會後回應時直認「我睇緊呢個Google Map，有好多資訊可以睇得到」，坦言有觀看香港和日本的資訊。<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸會後得悉事件後表示，知道不用發言的官員，長時間坐在會議廳可能很容易會入睡，「但唔好忘記，佢哋個個都收20幾、30萬公帑一個月，佢哋唔留心個會議，我覺得係對市民唔住」。<br />\n■記者林俊謙"},{"pid":"9fe66239a05f5d182d450224b2163c05fb984a72","tid":210499,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170421/large/21la8p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F21la8p4.jpg&h=0dafdd69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd11ff9c0cce41c9696e0b9e43b8c2dcccf1825e","tid":210499,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩個立法會，<br />\n<br />\n你報唔報都係咁過嫁啦, 程序黎姐。"}]}